        <div class="verse-group">
            <div class="ayah">١. أَلَمْ تَرَ كَيْفَ فَعَلَ رَبُّكَ بِأَصْحَابِ الْفِيلِ</div>
            <div class="translation">1. Have you (O Muhammad) not seen how your Lord dealt with the Owners of the Elephant?</div>
        </div>
        <div class="verse-group">
            <div class="ayah">٢. أَلَمْ يَجْعَلْ كَيْدَهُمْ فِي تَضْلِيلٍ</div>
            <div class="translation">2. Did He not make their plot go astray?</div>
        </div>
        <div class="verse-group">
            <div class="ayah">٣. وَأَرْسَلَ عَلَيْهِمْ طَيْرًا أَبَابِيلَ</div>
            <div class="translation">3. And He sent against them birds in flocks,</div>
        </div>
        <div class="verse-group">
            <div class="ayah">٤. تَرْمِيهِمْ بِحِجَارَةٍ مِّن سِجِّيلٍ</div>
            <div class="translation">4. Striking them with stones of baked clay.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="verse-group">
            <div class="ayah">٥. فَجَعَلَهُمْ كَعَصْفٍ مَّأْكُولٍ</div>
            <div class="translation">5. And made them like eaten straw.</div>
        </div>
